summary: This show Aggretsuko on Netflix is both the oddest but cutest thing in the world, ok?
body:
This show Aggretsuko on Netflix is both the oddest but cutest thing in the world, ok?

Cannot deny I feel Retsuko. Friends see her as cute, kind and reliable. Which is fine, but then there’s that side that completely loses it up to the point where you cannot possibly be the same being anymore lol.

summary: I decided to start posting drawings of mine just for fun! It’ll range from some of my original characters to actual characters...
body: I decided to start posting drawings of mine just for fun! It’ll range from some of my original characters to actual characters (from video games, anime, etc.) I hope to improve along the way, but for now I’ll just have fun with it! This is my first artwork of Retsuko and Haida, from an anime called “Aggretsuko”! I’m sorry that I have a limited supply of markers!!! Hope you like it! 😁
